05:38.972 --> 05:42.007
Have you ever seen a haunting this bad?!

05:42.075 --> 05:45.611
This is no
run-of-the-mill haunting!

05:45.679 --> 05:48.881
It's a poltergeist!

05:48.882 --> 05:52.084
A "ghost" only haunts a house.

05:52.185 --> 05:54.904
A poltergeist haunts a person!

05:54.905 --> 05:57.623
They're usually attracted to the

05:57.691 --> 06:03.535
terrifying inner world of
the emotionally disturbed!

06:04.464 --> 06:06.966
You think stuff is coming after me?!

06:07.033 --> 06:09.101
How can you listen to this weird guy?

06:09.169 --> 06:11.904
He practically lives in a haunted house.

06:11.972 --> 06:15.174
Don't you think maybe he had
something to do with it?

06:15.241 --> 06:19.345
I think you can stop
being such a dink to Ronaldo.

06:20.974 --> 06:23.315
Sadie, you're not an idiot!

06:23.383 --> 06:26.289
<i>- Hey!
- Do you believe all of this?!</i>

06:26.324 --> 06:28.454
- I...
- All this stuff ... they've got

06:28.521 --> 06:31.991
to be doing it somehow.
We've got to ditch these guys.

06:32.092 --> 06:33.577
Come on.

06:35.378 --> 06:37.062
I'm not ditching anyone.

06:37.130 --> 06:40.366
But what about me, huh?!
Sadie, come on. You always ...

06:40.433 --> 06:43.786
Huh?

06:45.933 --> 06:48.854
- Sadie?
- The spirit took her!

06:48.855 --> 06:51.276
You're gonna drag us all down

06:51.344 --> 06:53.078
with you!
Don't you even care?!

06:53.146 --> 06:56.298
<i>Lars!</i>

06:56.299 --> 06:59.451
The basement!

06:59.519 --> 07:04.223
- I don't see her anywhere!
- Spirit, show yourself!

07:04.290 --> 07:06.992
It's close. I can feel it.

07:07.093 --> 07:11.755
It's hurting and... obsessed.

07:16.069 --> 07:19.628
- It should've been you!
- Wh-What?

07:19.663 --> 07:22.178
It took her, but it should
have been you, Lars!

07:22.213 --> 07:24.009
Whoa!
H-Hold on, Ronaldo.

07:24.077 --> 07:28.180
<i>Lars.</i>

07:32.352 --> 07:35.487
- Hey! Let go!
- Wait! Stop!

07:35.555 --> 07:37.990
What are you doing?

07:38.091 --> 07:43.028
Spirit, I deliver the package
of darkness!

07:43.096 --> 07:46.796
Return to us the innocent Sadie!

07:46.797 --> 07:49.263
<i>Lars!</i>

07:49.298 --> 07:51.970
C-Come on, man.
We used to be friends.

07:52.038 --> 07:55.107
And you threw me away!

07:55.208 --> 07:57.609
- Lars!
- No, Steven!

07:57.677 --> 08:00.779
- He's not worth it!
- Why does everything bad

08:00.880 --> 08:04.749
happen to me?

08:15.895 --> 08:18.530
<i>Sadie!</i>

08:18.598 --> 08:23.469
It's a gem.

08:23.536 --> 08:29.007
<i>This is the perfect clubhouse
for the Beach City explorer club!</i>

08:29.109 --> 08:31.110
<i>Secret clubhouse, right, Ronny?</i>

08:31.177 --> 08:33.261
<i>Zip!</i>

08:37.951 --> 08:41.553
<i>Lars, you're a riot!</i>

08:41.621 --> 08:45.891
<i>- Dude!
- Just carving our names in!</i>

08:45.959 --> 08:50.496
<i>Pretty metal, huh?</i>

08:50.563 --> 08:53.298
<i>Weird.</i>

08:52.299 --> 08:57.068
<i>Holy smokes!</i>

08:57.103 --> 08:59.104
<i>The clubhouse is possessed!</i>

08:59.205 --> 09:02.141
<i>Lars! Lars!
When you turn on the TV</i>

09:02.208 --> 09:05.544
<i>tomorrow, this is what's
gonna be on every station!</i>

09:05.612 --> 09:08.814
<i>B-B-But ... but you
said this was secret.</i>

09:08.882 --> 09:11.283
<i>Our first paranormal discovery!</i>

09:11.351 --> 09:15.454
<i>We're gonna take on the world together!</i>

09:15.522 --> 09:20.359
<i>Um... let me just ...
uh, I'll just, uh...</i>

09:20.426 --> 09:24.325
<i>No!
What are you doing?!</i>

09:24.360 --> 09:27.280
<i>- No, no, no, no, no!
- I'm just tearing myself out.</i>

09:27.315 --> 09:29.501
<i>Stop!</i>

09:29.569 --> 09:33.138
<i>Let me... see!</i>

09:33.206 --> 09:35.948
<i>What did you do?
Oh!</i>

09:35.983 --> 09:38.277
<i>Oh, come on.
Ronny, know I can't let </i>

09:38.378 --> 09:40.245
<i>- people see me like that.
- What?!</i>

09:40.313 --> 09:41.764
<i>What's the matter with you?!</i>

09:41.765 --> 09:44.983
<i>Don't you know how important
this was?!</i>

09:48.321 --> 09:51.156
<i>Why do you care so much about</i>

09:51.224 --> 09:54.259
<i>- what other people think?!
- You wouldn't say that if you</i>

09:54.327 --> 09:57.429
<i>knew what other people say about you!</i>

10:04.103 --> 10:06.271
<i>Lars?</i>

10:08.508 --> 10:11.952
Okay, shh. I've got you.

10:11.987 --> 10:15.731
When you were stuck in the wall,
was the house like your body?

10:15.732 --> 10:17.349
You must have felt like you were

10:17.417 --> 10:20.185
under attack, back when
carved his Lars carved

10:20.253 --> 10:23.589
- his name in you.
- Can I see that?

10:23.656 --> 10:28.961
Uh, sorry.
We should let it rest.

10:29.062 --> 10:33.465
So, all that lashing out was
just from feeling hurt

10:33.533 --> 10:37.928
- and trapped for so long.
- I didn't mean to rip it up, okay?

10:37.963 --> 10:39.438
You can stop talking

10:39.505 --> 10:41.540
- about me now.
- Wait!

10:41.641 --> 10:45.911
- Oh, Sadie, are you okay?
- Uh, yeah. I'm fine.

10:46.012 --> 10:47.246
Oh, yeah.

10:47.313 --> 10:49.882
We were both worried about ...

10:49.883 --> 10:52.451
I mean, I ran down here faster.

10:52.518 --> 10:55.887
- Can we get out of here?
- Sadie, you can

10:55.955 --> 10:58.257
come with me.
I think these two have

10:58.324 --> 11:00.604
- a lot to talk about.
- I bet.

11:00.639 --> 11:02.951
I wasn't trying to make you
look bad.

11:02.986 --> 11:04.802
Ah, whatever.
It didn't matter.

11:04.837 --> 11:07.309
- I don't care!
- Hey, Lars...

11:07.344 --> 11:09.923
take it down a notch.

